sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant HAProxy as OpenShift Route<br/>HAProxy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Service as odh-dashboard Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant OAuthServer as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS
    participant NotebookCtrl as Kubeflow Notebook Controller

    %% Flow 1: User Authentication
    Note over User,Backend: Flow 1: User Authentication and Dashboard Access
    User->>HAProxy: GET /<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    HAProxy->>Service: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS Reencrypt
    Service->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+ (service cert)
    OAuth->>OAuthServer: Validate session/Redirect login<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>OAuth client credentials
    OAuthServer-->>OAuth: OAuth token + user identity
    OAuth->>Backend: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080 localhost<br/>Header: x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend-->>OAuth: Static frontend assets
    OAuth-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>HAProxy: Response
    HAProxy-->>User: HTML + JavaScript

    %% Flow 2: Backend API to Kubernetes
    Note over User,NotebookCtrl: Flow 2: Backend API to Kubernetes API
    User->>HAProxy: GET /api/components<br/>Bearer Token
    HAProxy->>Service: Forward
    Service->>OAuth: Forward with token
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/datasciencecluster.opendatahub.io/v1<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: DataScienceCluster status
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON response
    OAuth-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>HAProxy: Response
    HAProxy-->>User: Component status JSON

    %% Flow 3: Metrics Query
    Note over User,Thanos: Flow 3: Metrics Query to Prometheus/Thanos
    User->>HAProxy: POST /api/prometheus<br/>PromQL query<br/>Bearer Token
    HAProxy->>Service: Forward
    Service->>OAuth: Forward with token
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>Thanos: POST /api/v1/query<br/>HTTPS/9092 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: User Bearer Token (forwarded)
    Thanos-->>Backend: Prometheus metrics data
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON response
    OAuth-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>HAProxy: Response
    HAProxy-->>User: Metrics JSON

    %% Flow 4: Notebook Management
    Note over User,NotebookCtrl: Flow 4: Notebook Management
    User->>HAProxy: POST /api/notebooks<br/>Create notebook request<br/>Bearer Token
    HAProxy->>Service: Forward
    Service->>OAuth: Forward with token
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/kubeflow.org/v1/namespaces/{ns}/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook CR created
    K8sAPI->>NotebookCtrl: Watch event: Notebook created
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet<br/>Service Account Token
    Backend-->>OAuth: Success response
    OAuth-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>HAProxy: Response
    HAProxy-->>User: Notebook created JSON
